WEBVTT

00:01:28.318 --> 00:01:30.826
au biashara italazimika kua
na majibu,

00:01:30.850 --> 00:01:34.223
au kuna uwoga kua hawataweza?

00:01:34.247 --> 00:01:35.719
FC: Nadhani wataweza.

00:01:35.719 --> 00:01:37.237
Angalia wiki mbili zilizopita,

00:01:37.237 --> 00:01:41.837
kampuni ndogo iitwayo Skip
iliyoshinda Uber na Lyft na kila mtu

00:01:41.852 --> 00:01:47.094
ili ki halisi kupata leseni
kwa biashara ya pikipiki San Francisco.

00:01:47.124 --> 00:01:49.622
Na kama ukisoma kwanini Skip ilishinda,

00:01:49.622 --> 00:01:52.358
kwa sababu Skip ilisikiliza
watu wa San Francisco,

00:01:52.370 --> 00:01:55.126
waliokua wamechoka pikipiki
kua kila mahali,

00:01:55.140 --> 00:01:57.679
na kweli kwenda mjini na kusema,

00:01:57.679 --> 00:01:59.933
"Tutapeleka hio huduma,

00:01:59.953 --> 00:02:02.999
lakini tutajibu
mahitaji ya watu